dict.acceptation: 接来（某人）；使发出；吸引；售得（若干价钱）；
抵达，到达；取来；卖得（好价钱）；

sent.orig: The name of the macro-instruction(FETCH) used to accomplish1, 2, 3, or4.
sent.trans: 完成上述1，2，3或4动作的宏指令(FETCH)名。

sent.orig: Should I fetch you your coat/fetch your coat for you from the next room?
sent.trans: 要我去隔壁房间把你的大衣拿来吗？

sent.orig: The big monkey said: "Gosh! How can't they fetch water in such a long time? "
sent.trans: 大猴子说：“哎，怎么这么半天还没打好水？”

sent.orig: Go straight down to this Y.W.C.A. hostel and fetch Huei-fang home!
sent.trans: 你马上到女青年会寄宿舍去同四妹来！

sent.orig: Come to pay the fare and fetch your ticket 2 days before departure, please.
sent.trans: 请于起飞前2天来付款取票。
